thumb.title: 【足立レイ】リレイアウター 【OpenUtau カバー】
thumb.description: relayouter is so good i think more people should listen to it. . .So i got open utau yesterday and I really love Adachi Rei, so she was the first vocal i got! she’s so fucking fun to use like holy moly. I will say this cover was a pain in the ass to mix, but i also can’t mix for shit LOL. especially the slowed part..mv made by me, heavily inspired by the original
